{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2015-06-01-global-search-box-as-question-answering","webpackCompilationHash":"f141a48750e2a6a883f2","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"kevinhakanson.com","author":"Kevin Hakanson"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4a37db93-906c-5b9e-981a-c4d3dd7c938c","excerpt":"During a product design session, we had a discussion on Global Search covering “what search is” and “what search should be.”  I used the following example of…","html":"<p>During a product design session, we had a discussion on Global Search covering “what search is” and “what search should be.”  I used the following example of question answering as where I see “global search” heading:</p>\n<hr>\n<p>I can search Google for <strong>US population</strong> and it will give me an answer</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/30051/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.40650406504065%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Google &quot;US population&quot;\"\n        title=\"Google &quot;US population&quot;\"\n        src=\"/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/cf440/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png 148w,\n/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/d2d38/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png 295w,\n/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png 590w,\n/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/f9b6a/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png 885w,\n/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/2d849/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png 1180w,\n/static/148a4706e6bad2d0e412131f5fa5c119/30051/Google%2B-%2BUS%2Bpopulation.png 1599w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I can also search for <strong>2014 google revenue</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/1165a/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.35400516795866%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Google &quot;2014 google revenue&quot;\"\n        title=\"Google &quot;2014 google revenue&quot;\"\n        src=\"/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/cf440/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png 148w,\n/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/d2d38/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png 295w,\n/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png 590w,\n/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/f9b6a/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png 885w,\n/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/2d849/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png 1180w,\n/static/7dd90805fc6bedd8149a7c9a8b0352c7/1165a/Google%2B-%2Brevenue.png 1548w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I can even ask Google about revenue in the form of a question: <strong>how much money did google make in 2014</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/ca44b/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.181347150259064%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Google &quot;how much money did google make in 2014&quot;\"\n        title=\"Google &quot;how much money did google make in 2014&quot;\"\n        src=\"/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/cf440/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png 148w,\n/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/d2d38/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png 295w,\n/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png 590w,\n/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/f9b6a/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png 885w,\n/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/2d849/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png 1180w,\n/static/b62c6a25c3a21fe1e6dca78e40826bc1/ca44b/Google%2B-%2Bhow.png 1544w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>However, when I asked a question requiring a computation, I got search results and not an answer:  <strong>2014 google revenue per US population</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/ca44b/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.69430051813472%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Google &quot;2014 google revenue per US population&quot;\"\n        title=\"Google &quot;2014 google revenue per US population&quot;\"\n        src=\"/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/cf440/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png 148w,\n/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/d2d38/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png 295w,\n/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/b9e4f/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png 590w,\n/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/f9b6a/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png 885w,\n/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/2d849/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png 1180w,\n/static/822be15f2b50403ba3b9f249310787de/ca44b/Google%2B-%2Brevenue%2Bper%2BUS.png 1544w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>When I ask WolframAlpha that same question, I got an answer:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/93d99/WolframAlpha.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 99.77802441731409%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"WolframAlpha &quot;2014 google revenue per US population&quot;\"\n        title=\"WolframAlpha &quot;2014 google revenue per US population&quot;\"\n        src=\"/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/b9e4f/WolframAlpha.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/cf440/WolframAlpha.png 148w,\n/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/d2d38/WolframAlpha.png 295w,\n/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/b9e4f/WolframAlpha.png 590w,\n/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/f9b6a/WolframAlpha.png 885w,\n/static/0b5f1eef2099395704d6543048e588c0/93d99/WolframAlpha.png 901w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Global Search Box as Question Answering","date":"June 01, 2015","tags":["search","ux","nlp"]}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2015-06-01-global-search-box-as-question-answering","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2015-04-10-webstorm-10-and-typescript-support"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["javascript","typescript","webdev"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2015-06-03-azure-search-as-a-service"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["azure","search","nlp"]}}}}}